    pc "Ingeniería Cuántica."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:12
translate spanish kendraq2_980747ab:

    # sg "What the fuck is that?"
    sg "¿Qué coño es eso?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:13
translate spanish kendraq2_3a8c565d:

    # pc "Basically it's using mechanics, electrical engineering, systems and computer science on a quantum level."
    pc "Básicamente es aplicar la mecánica, la ingeniería eléctrica, los sistemas y la informática a nivel cuántico."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:15
translate spanish kendraq2_07512f82:

    # sg "Oh yeah, that sounds very basic."
    sg "Ah, sí, eso suena muy básico."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:16
translate spanish kendraq2_a677c2e3:

    # sg "Okay, nevermind, I get it. You're really smart."
    sg "Vale, da igual, ya lo pillo. Eres muy listo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:18
translate spanish kendraq2_d422f9ed:

    # sg "I didn't even know that they had a program for that junk at Skyhill."
    sg "Ni siquiera sabía que tuvieran un programa para esa mierda en Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:19
translate spanish kendraq2_0d17cf9b:

    # pc "They don't really. I took most of my advanced science classes down in Brazil."
    pc "En realidad no lo tienen. Cursé la mayor parte de mis asignaturas avanzadas de ciencias en Brasil."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:21
translate spanish kendraq2_a42901ac:

    # sg "You went to school in Brazil?"
    sg "¿Estudiaste en Brasil?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:22
translate spanish kendraq2_8ac9ae92:

    # pc "Yeah, for three years. I just came back."
    pc "Sí, durante tres años. Acabo de volver."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:24
translate spanish kendraq2_86b07fa7:

    # sg "Why the fuck would you want to come back here?"
    sg "¿Por qué coño querrías volver aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:25
translate spanish kendraq2_03fd43c1:

    # pc "My dad went missing. I came home to help find him."
    pc "Mi padre desapareció. Volví a casa para ayudar a encontrarlo."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:26
translate spanish kendraq2_3f912939:

    # sg "Did you find him?"
    sg "¿Lo has encontrado?"

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:27
translate spanish kendraq2_0b7558fc:

    # pc "Not yet."
    pc "Todavía no."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:29
translate spanish kendraq2_23ae1b3d:

    # sg "Aw that sucks. Sorry, man."
    sg "Vaya, qué pena. Lo siento, tío."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:30
translate spanish kendraq2_44963082:

    # sg "Back to Brazil though. That place seems so cool. I'd love to go there some day."
    sg "Pero volviendo a Brasil. Ese sitio parece genial. Me encantaría ir algún día."

# game/Scenes/Kendra/KendraConversations/kendraq2.rpy:31
translate spanish kendraq2_9c2ffa8e:

    # pc "It was pretty cool yeah. Beautiful country."
    pc "Sí, estaba muy bien. Es un país precioso."

